README
-----

Gnoll is a free (as free speech) 3D action/rpg game engine still at an early 
development stage.
The source code is under GNU/GPL v2 or greater. 

You can contact the development team at:
Gnoll Devel <gnoll-devel@gna.org>

======================================
Building Gnoll
======================================

In order to build Gnoll you will need these packages :
- Autotools
- g++
- libxml++2.6
- glibmm
- Ogre 3d 1.4.x 
- CEGUI 0.5.0
- OIS 1.0rc1
- boost_filesystem
- boost_thread
- OpenAL
- alut
- vorbis
- vorbisfile
- ogg
- sndfile
- boost_program_options


To build it, just launch these commands :
./bootstrap
./configure
make
make install


